<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/election-theft-is-a-120-year-tradition-lets-end-it-this-year/">Election Theft Is a 120-Year Tradition. Letâ€™s End It This Year.</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">We can&#8217;t depend on the Democratic Party to fight back. We need a grassroots movement to protect the voter rolls.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/bob-fitrakis/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Bob Fitrakis</a></span> & </dd>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/harvey-wasserman/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Harvey Wasserman</a></span>, </dd>
